
The Season of Men  ni filime y'ikinamico yo mu 2000 y’Abafaransa-Tuniziya iyobowe na Moufida Tlatli<ref>The Season of Men - Rotten Tomatoes</ref> . Yerekanwe mu gice cya Un Certain Regard mu iserukiramuco rya sinema rya Cannes 2000<ref>The Season of Men - KVIFF <nowiki>https://www.kviff.com</nowiki> › programme › film › 18241-th...</ref> .  Umutwe wa filime, Igihe cy'abagabo, werekeza ukwezi kumwe kwumwaka abagabo  baza ku kirwa cya Djerba<ref>THE SEASON OF MEN - İstanbul Modern <nowiki>https://www.istanbulmodern.org</nowiki> › cinema › the-season-...</ref>. 

