== Umugambi ==
Umusore w'imyaka 18 ku kirwa cya Djerba, Aïcha, yashakanye na Said, ukora muri Tuniziya igihe kinini cy'umwaka<ref>The Season of Men | Film Review | Spirituality & Practice (spiritualityandpractice.com)</ref>. Mbere yuko ashobora kubana na we muri Tuniziya, Said amusaba ko yamuha umuhungu<ref>FILM REVIEW; Married but Seldom With a Husband <nowiki>https://www.nytimes.com</nowiki> › 2001/09/28 › movies › film-r...</ref>.  Ku kirwa cya Djerba, Aïcha abaho ategekwa na nyirabukwe, hamwe n'abandi bagore bake, mu gihe abagabo babo bakorera ahandi<ref>The Season of Men - Variety <nowiki>https://variety.com</nowiki> › the-season-of-men-1117780961</ref>. Aïcha yaje kubyara umuhungu kandi yemerewe kwimukira muri Tuniziya hamwe n'umugabo we. Ariko, umuhungu we Aziz afite ibibazo by'ubuzima, bigatuma Saïd amwanga. Aïcha asubira i Djerba, kuri iyi nshuro ari kumwe n'umuhungu we Aziz n'abakobwa be babiri bakuru<ref>The Season of Men Reviews - Metacritic <nowiki>https://www.metacritic.com</nowiki> › movie › the-season-of-men</ref>. Iyi filime ikoresha ibintu byinshi byagaragaye hagati ya Aïcha n’abakobwa be bato batuye i Djerba mbere y’ivuka rya Aziz hanyuma igaragara muri iki gihe, aho Aziz afite imyaka umunani, mbere yuko asubira i Djerba<ref>Moufida Tlatli, Groundbreaker in Arab Film, Dies at 78 <nowiki>https://www.nytimes.com</nowiki> › moufida-tlatli-dead-coronavirus</ref>. Filime irangira Aïcha na Aziz bakorana bombi bakora imyenda, bakora kaseti Aïcha agurisha. Filime irangira umukobwa muto wa Aïcha Emna agenda, Aïcha na Aziz babana i Djerba<ref>Moufida Tlatli, Silences of the Palace director, dies aged 73 | Film | The Guardian</ref>.
